<h2 class="title mb-40">PRIVACY POLICY: </h2>
<h4 class="sm-title">Your Consent:</h4>
By clicking on Qalpedu.com (https://www.Qalpedu.com) and accessing its services/ products on a continual basis as a visitor or a member, you expressly consent to Qalpedu.com’s terms of Collecting, Maintaining, Using, Processing, and Disclosing your personal data along with other information in accordance toits Privacy Policies and Data protection.
<h4 class="sm-title">Commitment:</h4>
Qalpedu.com.com intends to protect the privacy along with the data protection of its esteemed customers availing their services on the digital platformfrom time to time. The privacy of our online users, irrespective of being a former or existing registered member else a visitor to the website, are considered pivotal and hence we, at Qalpedu.com strongly commit to securing our customers right to privacy and protection of personal and other valuable information provided. 
For the purpose of serving our customers better, our website gathers preliminary personal datain order to identify you as a user in and to understand your requirements. Some of our services may direct you to web domains of third parties. However, this Privacy Policy concentratesonly in regards to the data shared with Qalpedu.com (Registered member/ Visitor) and we shall in no means be liable/bound for protection of information (if any), which may be shared by you on any such third-party web domains.
What kinds of information does Kalp-Educare collect from you?

<h4 class="sm-title">Personal Information:</h4>
