If you are a Prospective customer (Student/ Parent/ Guardian) looking to connect with Qalpedu.com professionals, our website registers your Name, Email ID, Personal contact number, Personal interest/Preferences and Location. Data recorded is shared on a limited basis with our Qalpedu.com Professionals upon filtration based on preferences to facilitate faster connect between both parties. Furthermore, in order to initiate certain transactions against services provided, our website may also require you to submit your Credit card/ Debit card/ Bank account details through a secure Third-Party Payment Gateway provider. In case of NEFT transfers, we shall request your bank details and transactions ID to confirm the payment. Such information is strictly confidential and limited even to our team as well. 
In addition, Qalpedu.com also records voluntary data such as Feedbacks, Suggestions, Views, Comments, Blogs etc. shared on various discussion forums or pages published on the website for public viewing (Accessible by Members/ Viewers).In this regard, you are advised to exercise discretion before you make such details public, as such information may be vulnerable to misuse and can be easily misused.Qaledu.com in this regard fully disclaims any liability(ies) or claim(s) which may arise by use/misuse of such information shared by you, by any third party or any party not known to Qalpedu.
For Qalpedu.com to recognize you as a registered member,it is required of you to login with your Mobile no. and one time secured Password.Qalpedu.com ensures our customers’ login credentials are highly confidential and are never shared within or outside of Qalpedu.com under any circumstances.Other data such as written communications, email reverts, feedbacks, discussions etc. shall be deemed to be confidential and shall be owned by Qalpedu.com and made available for the exclusive use of Qalpedu.com. Our website does not forcefully attain any personal information unless consciously provided by its customers. Qalpedu.com DOES NOT and WILL NOT trade or sell your information in any manner, except as specified herein, or if express consent is sought from you in written.

<h4 class="sm-title">Promotional Initiatives:</h4>

<p>Qalpedu.com presence on social networking platforms including but not limited to LinkedIn, Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, YouTube, Google Plus, etc. is merely a promotional initiative to invite registrations and participation of prospective customers located in various cities across the country. The domain links contained therein may either direct you to our website or request your active participation by means of feedback, suggestions. Qalpedu.com in this regard fully disclaims any liability(ies) or claim(s) which may arise by use/misuse of your valuable feedback, suggestions, views, etc. on any of the aforementioned networking websites or blogs, by any third party whether or not known to Qalpedu.com.</p>
<h4 class="sm-title">How does Qalpedu.com protect my Personal Information?</h4>
<p>Qalpedu.com is committed to protect the privacy and the confidentiality of your personal information. Whenever Qalpedu.com obtains personal data from its customers, our website uses commercially reasonable efforts and general industrial standards to protect the data from any unauthorized access or disclosure. Save as otherwise provided herein, access to your personal information is limited to Qalpedu.com’s personnel and such authorized third parties who may host your data on our behalf or may assist us in providing the products and services requested by our clients. Qalpedu.com uses its best endeavours to maintain physical, electronic, and procedural safeguards that aim to protect customer information against loss, misuse, damage, modification, and unauthorized access or disclosure. However, Qalpedu.com undertakes no liability whatsoever for any disclosure of personal information due to unauthorized third-party access or other acts of third parties, or any other acts or omissions beyond reasonable control of Qalpedu.com</p>
<h4 class="sm-title">How does Qalpedu.com use the information that it collects?</h4>
<p>Client information may be used by Qalpedu.com.com and/or authorized third parties/service partners to support customer engagement and to best serve our customers by offering our services and products. By submitting your personal data to Qalpedu.com.com, you expressly consent to Qalpedu.com to utilize the attained data and to process the same in a manner ethically deemed to be fit by Qalpedu.com. This may involve conducting data analysis, research based on reviews about deals, transfer of your data to third party experts for the purpose of outsourcing services offered to you by Qalpedu.com, etc.
</p>
<p>What security precautions are in place to protect against the loss, misuse, or alteration of your information?</p>

<p>Qalpedu.com continuously ensures to preserve the privacy and confidentiality of customer information shared with us. We implement standard measures and mechanisms compliant with the applicable laws to protect against unauthorized access to and unlawful interception of your personal data. However, no Internet site can fully eliminate security risks.We reserve the right to disclose the information collected our customers without their consent (express or implied) and without prior notice when required or permitted by law and we have a bonafidebelief that-	</p>		
<p>(i) such action is necessary to comply with an appropriate law enforcement investigation,current judicial proceeding, a court order or legal process served on us.</p>
<p>(ii) to abibe to the legal requirements, compliance/reporting to administrative and judicial authorities, as and when required.</p>
<p>(iii) to protect and defend the rights or property of the website owners of Qalpedu.com, or the users of Qalpedu.com,</p>
<p>(iv) the person(s) or company(ies) who provide certain support services to us, and</p>

<p> (v)the person(s) or company(ies) who share certain responsibilities/obligations of Qalpedu.com</p>

